data.description: Large 1st Floor 2 bedroom and 2 bathroom condo at over 1400 sf! The den could possibly be turned into a 3rd bedroom. Unit includes a 1 car garage, and additional detached large storage space. The driveway to the garage is large enough for 1 vehicle. This unit even has a small covered patio with a new patio fence. Located in a gated community featuring pool, spa, & green spaces.  New refrigerator, microwave, washer and dryer, including many other new features.
